text:
Kaho...!
Can you wait a moment...!

I'm sorry!
I left you behind.

No, I'm the one who should apologize.
You're still full of energy, huh...!

You seem especially energetic today.
Is there something on your mind?

It's my first time here,
so I'm curious about everything!

It feels like I'm going on an adventure,
so I'm having fun...!

That's right! I want you to enjoy not just
the work, but also other aspects.
I'll do my best to keep up as much as possible!
